maintext:
INDIANAPOLIS (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon’s drawing of the Indiana Lottery’s “Quick Draw Midday” game were:
01-02-03-16-19-30-33-35-38-39-47-48-50-51-54-65-66-69-75-77, BE: 50
(one, two, three, sixteen, nineteen, thirty, thirty-three, thirty-five, thirty-eight, thirty-nine, forty-seven, forty-eight, fifty, fifty-one, fifty-four, sixty-five, sixty-six, sixty-nine, seventy-five, seventy-seven; BE: fifty)
